WEBVTT

00:00:01.480 --> 00:00:09.650
Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,
your uniqueness into strength

00:00:09.770 --> 00:00:17.900
Even if you get lost, let’s start walking

00:00:18.150 --> 00:00:20.190
One more time

00:00:23.150 --> 00:00:26.900
Are you really happy

00:00:26.940 --> 00:00:30.440
when you're always meeting
to someone's expectations?

00:00:30.650 --> 00:00:34.150
Even if you change to
who you really wanna be

00:00:34.570 --> 00:00:37.820
Will you always have a great smile?

00:00:37.860 --> 00:00:45.440
Dreaming of only “the beginning,”
I wake up

00:00:45.480 --> 00:00:54.690
and someday, I'll live on my own.

00:00:54.730 --> 00:01:02.770
Yes, precious things are never in shape

00:01:02.900 --> 00:01:09.770
You never know what it is
when you get it or lose it

00:01:09.780 --> 00:01:17.900
Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,
your uniqueness into strength

00:01:18.230 --> 00:01:26.770
Even if you get lost,
let's start walking

00:01:26.770 --> 00:01:28.770
One more time

00:01:55.770 --> 00:01:58.030
His opponent is that Neji, huh…?

00:01:58.530 --> 00:02:01.320
The Final Round is altogether different
than the preliminaries…

00:02:01.770 --> 00:02:03.610
After all, Naruto may not be able to…

00:02:23.030 --> 00:02:26.940
Entertain me a little, Naruto.

00:02:28.480 --> 00:02:32.690
I’ve got a tough job waiting
for me now, so…

00:02:34.190 --> 00:02:40.190
Ultimate Defense: Zero Blind Spot!

00:03:13.770 --> 00:03:16.480
Dang it. I can’t catch him at all.

00:03:18.940 --> 00:03:21.770
I told you I’m not
such a fool, didn’t I?

00:03:28.770 --> 00:03:32.780
I already know…
which one is the real one.

00:03:39.030 --> 00:03:39.770
Oh.

00:03:40.110 --> 00:03:42.820
That is the body
that has least attacks

00:03:42.860 --> 00:03:45.770
due to its fear of having
Chakra Points attacked.

00:03:46.110 --> 00:03:48.610
The more you attack,

00:03:48.650 --> 00:03:50.650
the more that one body
becomes clearly evident.

00:03:54.320 --> 00:03:55.980
You’re the real one.

00:03:56.360 --> 00:03:57.530
Naruto…

00:03:57.900 --> 00:03:59.360
This is as far as it goes.

00:04:04.440 --> 00:04:06.360
I said it was pointless.

00:04:09.230 --> 00:04:11.770
Don’t let him beat you, Naruto.

00:04:16.610 --> 00:04:21.400
I’ve been telling you not
to frivolously assume things.

00:04:22.940 --> 00:04:23.730
What?

00:04:24.570 --> 00:04:25.400
It can’t be.

00:04:30.780 --> 00:04:33.730
All right! Go, Naruto!

00:04:34.900 --> 00:04:35.820
Naruto…!

00:04:36.690 --> 00:04:41.570
