the body of the Hyuga head family

00:20:13.480 --> 00:20:16.320
who possesses Byakugan,
the Kekkei Genkai…

00:20:17.360 --> 00:20:21.070
In other words,
the body of Lord Hiashi.

00:20:23.770 --> 00:20:26.530
And the Leaf accepted the condition.

00:20:26.860 --> 00:20:29.320
